'''Elaine''' is a worker at a food truck that was affected by a rocket crash.

==History==
Elaine was working at a food truck when a rocket crashed nearby and caused a set of small fires near the food trucks. Elaine was minority injured in this accident and was treated in the triage area. While she was recovering, Andy found a piece of metal nearby and asked if there was nearby tech campus. Elaine said there was, a bunch of math nerds with food allergies. Andy then determined the aircraft had been a rocket.

==Career==
She works at a food truck.
